Description: The Fragrance Foundation is the premiere resource for industry expertise, innovation and education. United under the mission statement “to inspire the world to discover the artistry and passion of fragrance,” The Foundation is devoted to nurturing talent, celebrating the creativity of perfumers and engaging consumers to in- crease appreciation for the world of fragrance.
